    "body": "### Problem\n\n`src/nvim/grid.c:672: grid_put_linebuf: Assertion `0 <= row && row < grid->rows' failed.`\n\n```cpp\n#0  __pthread_kill_implementation (threadid=<optimized out>, signo=signo@entry=6, no_tid=no_tid@entry=0) at ./nptl/pthread_kill.c:44\n#1  0x00007f6bc529847f in __pthread_kill_internal (threadid=<optimized out>, signo=6) at ./nptl/pthread_kill.c:89\n#2  0x00007f6bc5241942 in __GI_raise (sig=sig@entry=6) at ../sysdeps/posix/raise.c:26\n#3  0x00007f6bc52294ac in __GI_abort () at ./stdlib/abort.c:77\n#4  0x00007f6bc5229420 in __assert_fail_base (fmt=<optimized out>, assertion=<optimized out>, file=<optimized out>, line=<optimized out>, function=0x55d565b597f0 <__PRETTY_FUNCTION__.3> \"grid_put_linebuf\") at ./assert/assert.c:118\n#5  0x000055d5657d74d0 in grid_put_linebuf (grid=0x55d565cbe820 <default_grid>, row=17, coloff=0, col=37, endcol=81, clear_width=81, bg_attr=0, clear_attr=0, last_vcol=-1, flags=0)\n    at .../src/nvim/grid.c:672\n#6  0x000055d5657d728f in grid_line_flush () at .../src/nvim/grid.c:600\n#7  0x000055d5659e930e in do_intro_line (row=17, mesg=0x55d565bb67a8 \"type  :help Kuwasha<Enter>  for information \", colon=true, is_logo=false) at .../src/nvim/version.c:4351\n#8  0x000055d5659e8e96 in intro_message (colon=true) at .../src/nvim/version.c:4255\n#9  0x000055d5659e932b in ex_intro (eap=0x7fff2625a6a0) at .../src/nvim/version.c:4361\n#10 0x000055d56578fca9 in execute_cmd0 (retv=0x7fff2625a658, eap=0x7fff2625a6a0, errormsg=0x7fff2625a670, preview=false) at .../src/nvim/ex_docmd.c:1782\n#11 0x000055d565791d45 in do_one_cmd (cmdlinep=0x7fff2625a8c0, flags=11, cstack=0x7fff2625a9d0, fgetline=0x0, cookie=0x0) at .../src/nvim/ex_docmd.c:2411\n#12 0x000055d56578d1e5 in do_cmdline (cmdline=0x7fff2625c798 \"intro\", fgetline=0x0, cookie=0x0, flags=11) at .../src/nvim/ex_docmd.c:679\n#13 0x000055d56578c73a in do_cmdline_cmd (cmd=0x7fff2625c798 \"intro\") at .../src/nvim/ex_docmd.c:377\n#14 0x000055d5658445b1 in exe_commands (parmp=0x7fff2625afe0) at .../src/nvim/main.c:2024\n#15 0x000055d56584042f in main (argc=4, argv=0x7fff2625b248) at .../src/nvim/main.c:625\n```\n\n### Steps to reproduce\n\n`nvim --clean -c 'se lines=17' -c intro`\n\n### Expected behavior\n\nNo crash\n\n### Nvim version (nvim -v)\n\nv0.12.0-dev-2646+g9595f07425\n\n### Vim (not Nvim) behaves the same?\n\nn/a\n\n### Operating system/version\n\nDebian Sid\n\n### Terminal name/version\n\nalacritty\n\n### $TERM environment variable\n\nalacritty\n\n### Installation\n\nfrom repo",
